PrecisConfirmation of a SPECIFIC AGREEMENT between the Crown, the Province of Ontario and THE EABAMETOONG FIRST NATION (formerly the Fort Hope Indian Band) whereby the Province releases and quit claims unto Canada, for the use and benefit of the Band, any and all rights it has or may have in the mines and minerals on Fort Hope Indian Reserve No. 64, including any revenues or royalties derived therefrom.
